@startuml
title Gambar 5.16 Sequence Diagram Kelola Data Aset

actor User
participant "Asset Page" as AssetPage
participant "Aset API" as AsetAPI
participant "Auth Middleware" as AuthMiddleware
database "Aset Model" as AsetModel
participant "Audit Service" as AuditService

User -> AssetPage: Mengisi atau memperbarui data aset
AssetPage -> AsetAPI: Request create/update/delete aset
AsetAPI -> AuthMiddleware: Validasi token dan permission
AuthMiddleware --> AsetAPI: Akses valid
AsetAPI -> AsetModel: Menyimpan perubahan data
AsetModel --> AsetAPI: Data berhasil diproses
AsetAPI -> AuditService: Mencatat aktivitas
AsetAPI --> AssetPage: Respons sukses
AssetPage --> User: Menampilkan konfirmasi

@enduml
